{"tid":1507120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇番所有莫須有的拘捕時間係為左 10.1","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:56:48.000Z","uid":70964,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"573c91a25b86074b095165564eec88df4f90d192","tid":1507120,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"發現到而家拘捕左之後兩日後即刻提堂<br />\n而被捕者 都要服從宵禁令 ( 一般兩個多月 ) 再提堂 <br />\n所以POPO 而家可以冇條件可以拉O左先 ( 為滅聲 ) <br />\n你睇麗晶單野已經知<br />\n私人屋苑都可以CHARGE 「在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家POPO可以有咩做唔出?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以慎重起見 以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不被捕</span></span>為第一原則<br />\n預先制訂逃走路線"},{"pid":"77c0f0abf9784293591826d3f083d6177a61f0a8","tid":1507120,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54f37b25bc77c510be4a0ea7a8e57a21e5fc1577","tid":1507120,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aDXx3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aDXx3V.jpg&h=d8b32aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f75015bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjbVjJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjbVjJ3.jpg&h=4677b5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f75015bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"fce94fbbe7d79a7f8e238d808b5c16a74f2c1135"